Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.38,0:00:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Karl!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have some time right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.85,0:00:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I just thought that maybe we \N could go out for tea or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we could also talk about the \N incidents involving Mr. Schuwald...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to do that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.15,0:00:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm kind of in a hurry right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.39,0:00:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father has to get to a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.29,0:00:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, about the dance party coming up...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.08,0:00:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to go... with me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:27.25,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,76)\pos(360,344)}Holy Ground
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to close soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.12,0:02:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's closing time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl's here again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pretty girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God is so unfair...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure a girl like her doesn't have any problems in life...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's closing time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen that girl somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dance party?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really care about these things, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my friends forced me to buy these.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but tonight's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The state legislature's holding a dinner meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not just a dinner meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there are a lot of people who would \N want to go with you to the dance party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not like I really wanted to go, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking up information on Margot Langer, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you don't have to clear the screen like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also doing research on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, data for my thesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a cultural anthropology major, Lotte Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty good, Ms. Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is "The Murder Case of the Accountant..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a newspaper article on "The Murder \N Case of the Voice of God..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is "The Murder Case of \N the Middle Aged Couple..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:04:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm pretty confident in my own \N information gathering, I'm no match for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm currently looking into Bayern's unsolved \N murders from the past four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell me more about the case of \N the former prostitute, Margot Langer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I've told you so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The son born of Margot Langer and \N the wealthy Hans Schuwald...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was finally happily recognized by Schuwald...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and has become his successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any chance of the son being involved in the \N incidents that occurred around Schuwald?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm 100% certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem enthusiastic about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're digging pretty deep for just \N a simple college research paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You think so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not for a research paper, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm searching for someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do people like you have problems, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm saying is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't everything in the world go the \N way you want when you're that pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,0:06:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For instance...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never had problems when \N it comes to love, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My problems have nothing to do with you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God really is unfair...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to hang out tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to a dance party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really like these kinds of places...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will talk to me if I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, everyone's looking this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just take the leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Lotte...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, here comes one now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Konstantin, from the Transcendental \N Phenomenon study group.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap.  One of those geeky ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised he had the guts to talk \N to you with that kind of face, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Lotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be my partner for tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Lotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not my type!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay with me, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're kind of alone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of guys have asked you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because you're being too cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't being cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's been a while since I've had this much fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I've been together with students...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and done stupid things with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really been a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty steadfast, despite your appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  What do you mean, "despite my appearance"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please dance with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A short one's fine.  Just a short one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're drunk, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:08:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I"m asking you because I want to, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just dance with me once!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can get my money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Money...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karl asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He asked me to be your partner for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karl...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So just dance a little with me.  That's all I ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one song...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!  Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!  I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!  Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I like Karl, I helped him find his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... liked him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But once he was able to prove that \N he was Schuwald's real son...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He kept saying he had something to do with his father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He kept saying he made a promise to his father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"His father" this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"His father" that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:11:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think being turned down would hurt so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes it hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything feels bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad things don't last long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't let it last so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me where I can reach you, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I haven't decided \N where I'm going to live yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then give me a call at my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really had fun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you find the one you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I'd seen her before...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks exactly like Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty good shot, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's probably due more to the \N efficiency of the gun, than your skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:13:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it failed the German military's \N test for being their official sniper rifle...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you can still hit a 5cm circle from 300m with that gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even as an amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're trying to shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the closer you get, the higher \N your chance of hitting it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is to pick a location free of \N obstacles between you and your target.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It uses .338 Lapua Magnum bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can hold a maximum of four bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you can't afford to shoot all four bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't finish it in one shot, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been coming here every single day recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here to bird watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.76,0:14:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every Thursday, this forest gets a lot of visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two young men with that old guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.19,0:14:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like this forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:14:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm apologizing to this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And have been for the past sixty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen him around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was proud of that dish, yet he didn't eat much of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get to the question so they can earn valuable prizes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our first contestant, Mr. Weidlich, comes from Frankfurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here's his prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a camper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what his family wanted most!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Weidlich seems really happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be great if he can go camping in this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, unless he answers ten questions correctly, \N he won't be able to win this camper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the first question!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to leave without touching your food again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came here about a week ago, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.20,0:17:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how busy we get, I still \N remember my customer's faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have an appetite, at least eat the soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.79,0:17:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:17:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to shoot him here in the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I slipped, after walking \N the same road all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must be getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you broke anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've given you first aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have it checked out at a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a doctor...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were a hunter when I first saw you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the birds...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.06,0:19:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The birds are gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, wild birds would perch \N on a certain man's shoulder...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he stretched out his arm like \N this, wild birds would land on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.03,0:20:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he was little, he used to spend all \N his time with the birds in this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, eventually, Hitler's era came.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man was stationed with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He truly believed that socialism and the Nazi party...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.78,0:20:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would make this the ideal country.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, he was given an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An atrocious criminal ran into this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was chosen to chase after the criminal \N because he was familiar with the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To shoot and kill the criminal on sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He chased the criminal through the forest \N that he knew like the back of his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He chased...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he chased...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he finally cornered him, he wasn't an atrocious \N criminal, but just a normal foreigner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no matter who the foreigner \N was, he had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He carried out his order.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.53,0:21:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, the birds have never perched on his shoulder...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.53,0:21:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been apologizing for sixty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.65,0:21:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.13,0:21:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the birds won't come near him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.07,0:21:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear God in Heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.91,0:22:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.47,0:22:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never again...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never again will blood be shed in this forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.87,0:22:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
